  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "This model has been applied in clinical research settings to predict hemolysis in centrifugal blood pumps. The CFD hemolysis model for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump was assessed under ventricular assist device operating conditions. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed across 13 credibility factors; 7 factors were formally assessed and 6 were flagged as epistemic gaps. Despite the gaps, aggregate credibility was judged sufficient for the intended engineering decision. No structured Context of Use record is attached; the intended-use scope is conveyed descriptively in this narrative only.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-cfd-claim-001",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/fda-centrifugal-pump-cfd-v2",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-pump-experimental-hemolysis-dataset",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-pump-cfd-output-dataset"
  ],
